---
// Hero Section Component
---

<section
    class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1055C9] via-[#05339C] to-[#0046FF] text-white py-10 md:py-20"
>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/10"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <!-- Left Content -->
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <div
                    class="inline-block bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold"
                >
                    Kuliah Kelas Karyawan
                </div>
                <h1
                    class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight"
                >
                    Upgrade Diri, Gaji, Jabatan, dan Karir untuk Masa Depan!
                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
                    Kuliah Kelas Karyawan adalah perkuliahan yang dikhususkan
                    untuk karyawan sibuk bekerja dan juga mereka yang ingin atau
                    sedang mencari pekerjaan sambil tetap kuliah. Kelas karyawan
                    dapat kuliah full online maupun offline.
                </p>
                <p class="text-base opacity-80">
                    Di Universitas STEKOM menyediakan program kuliah kelas
                    karyawan fleksibel serta biaya yang fleksibel, dengan begitu
                    memberikan alternatif supaya tetap bisa melanjutkan
                    pendidikan di sela kesibukan.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pt-4">
                    <a
                        href="https://stekom.ac.id/hal/promo-pmb-2025-kk"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-white text-[#1055C9] hover:bg-gray-100 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-105"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-5 h-5 mr-2"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                        Daftar Sekarang
                    </a>
                    <a
                        href="/hubungi-kami"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-[#1055C9] px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg transition-all duration-300"
                    >
                        <svg
                            class="w-5 h-5 mr-2"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                stroke-width="2"
                                d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                        Hubungi Kami
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Image/Illustration -->
            <div class="relative max-w-lg mx-auto lg:mx-0">
                <div
                    class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-4 md:p-6 border border-white/20"
                >
                    <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                        <img
                            src="/assets/images/thumbnail-kelas-karyawan-1024x683.jpg"
                            alt="Thumbnail Kelas Karyawan"
                            class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-center mt-3 text-xs md:text-sm opacity-75">
                        Universitas Sains dan Teknologi Komputer
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
